<asp:Content ID="MainContentPlaceHolderContent" ContentPlaceHolderID="MainContent"
    runat="Server">
    <div class="FaqContainer">
        <table width="96%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
            <tr>
                <td align="left" class="menuheading">
                    Frequently Asked Questions
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <hr size="1" noshade="noshade" color="#b4545f" />
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td align="left">
                    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                        <tr>
                            <td align="left" valign="top" class="style2">
                                <img src="images/FAQs.png" alt="" width="130" height="138" />
                            </td>
                            <td width="454" align="left" valign="top" class="bodytext2">
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    We have included some answers to popular questions:
                                </p>
                                <span class="smallheading">Why should I Order Online?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    Online ordering is a great way to make to takeaway orders. Some of the great reasons
                                    include:
                                    <br />
                                    » Clear Ordering The takeaway knows exactly what your have ordered, no need to complicated
                                    and confusing phone calls. » Online Special Offers Please see the special offers
                                    page.
                                    <br />
                                    » Easy Payment Pay easily and safely online (if available), or on collection/delivery.
                                    <br />
                                    » Save Time No need for a phone call or being put on hold, just select your dishes
                                    and complete the order, it is then sent straight to the restaurant.
                                    <br />
                                    » Reliable As soon as your order is place it is sent straight to the takeaway and
                                    you get confirmation email.
                                    <br />
                                    » Claim Back Expenses Ordering for the company? The itemised email/bill will allow
                                    you to easily claim the expenses.</p>
                                <span class="smallheading">Is my information safe?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    When you make an order we only ask you for the information we need to complete the
                                    order. This includes your contact details and your email address for collections,
                                    we only ask for your address if you want delivery or if you choose to pay online
                                    (only if this option is available). If paying by credit card, this is all handled
                                    by SAGEPAY, we record none of your credit card details. To speed up your ordering
                                    you need to register with us. We will never share this information with any third
                                    party. We take your privacy very serious, and if you have questions please contact
                                    us.</p>
                                <span class="smallheading">How do I pay?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    You can pay online or on collection/delivery. On collection/Delivery we only accept
                                    cash. Our drivers does not carry any card machine.
                                </p>
                                <span class="smallheading">What if I need to change my order?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    Before the order is completed you can change the order at any time by returning
                                    to the menu (don't worry your current order will not be lost). After the order is
                                    completed please contact us directly by using the phone number on the Contact Us
                                    Page.
                                </p>
                                <span class="smallheading">Do you have any Special Offers?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    To see current special offers, please view Deals page by clicking on the Deals link.
                                    We are always bringing out new special offers for online orders, this is why it
                                    is important to register. We will let you know as soon as more offers are available.
                                </p>
                                <span class="smallheading">How do I cancel my order?</span> </p>
                                <span class="style3">If you have not
                                completed the order on the website, you can cancel by simply leaving the website.
                                Make sure you logged out from your account in order to avoid any misuse of your
                                details. If you have already completed the order please contact us directly by using
                                the phone number on the Contact Us Page. </span> </p> <span class="smallheading">How do I leave
                                    feedback?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    If you have some comment about online ordering then why not visit our Facebook page.
                                    Here you can post on our wall and leave reviews.
                                </p>
                                <span class="smallheading">I have forgotten my password</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    Don't worry, simply click on the 'Forgot Password' link in login window and you
                                    will be sent a new password.</p>
                                <span class="smallheading">How do I track my order?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    If you register with us, you can simply go to Track Order page and view all your
                                    pending orders. We display your full order detail and status as well.
                                </p>
                                <span class="smallheading">Where are you?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    We have all our contact details on our Contact Us page. This includes our address,
                                    phone number, opening hours and a Google map of showing the location of the restaurant.
                                </p>
                                <span class="smallheading">Where do you Deliver?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    We generally offer delivery to the local area. If you do not see a delivery map
                                    then also long as you are within 4 miles of the restaurant we should be able to
                                    delivery. If in doubt please ring us or select Collection.
                                </p>
                                <span class="smallheading">How do I know the Wrapidos Leicester shop has received the order?</span>
                                <p style="color: #000000">
                                    Once you have placed your order on Wrapidos Leicester website it is instantly received by Wrapidos Leicester
                                     system. You get a confirmation email if your order is accepted or rejected.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <br />
                                </p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" align="left" valign="top">
                                &nbsp;
